{"sections":[],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"text":"@protocol","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"},{"text":" <","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:objc(pl)NSObject","text":"NSObject","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":">","kind":"text"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"overview","type":"heading","level":2,"text":"Overview"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An object that adopts this protocol must implement the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"coordinate"},{"type":"text","text":" property."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"The other methods of this protocol are optional."}]},{"anchor":"Related-examples","type":"heading","level":4,"text":"Related examples"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"TODO: Annotation models","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"TODO: Annotation views, learn how to add objects that follow the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"text":" protocol","type":"text"}]}]}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"type":"reference","isActive":true,"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"kind":"symbol","topicSections":[{"generated":true,"identifiers":["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation\/coordinate","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation\/subtitle","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation\/title"],"title":"Instance Properties","anchor":"Instance-Properties"}],"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"major":0,"patch":0},"metadata":{"role":"symbol","title":"MLNAnnotation","navigatorTitle":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}],"roleHeading":"Protocol","externalID":"c:objc(pl)MLNAnnotation","fragments":[{"text":"MLNAnnotation","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"MapLibre"}],"symbolKind":"protocol"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"relationshipsSections":[{"kind":"relationships","type":"inheritsFrom","identifiers":["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/objc(pl)NSObject"],"title":"Inherits From"},{"kind":"relationships","type":"inheritedBy","identifiers":["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNFeature","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOverlay"],"title":"Inherited By"},{"kind":"relationships","type":"conformingTypes","identifiers":["doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocation"],"title":"Conforming Types"}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation"},"references":{"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation/coordinate":{"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"coordinate"}],"title":"coordinate","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation\/coordinate","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The center point (specified as a map coordinate) of the annotation. (required)"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"(read-only)"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation\/coordinate","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation/subtitle":{"type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The string containing the annotation’s subtitle."}],"title":"subtitle","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"subtitle"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation\/subtitle","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation\/subtitle","role":"symbol","kind":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation/title":{"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"title"}],"title":"title","kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation\/title","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The string containing the annotation’s title."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation\/title","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNUserLocation":{"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNUserLocation"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocation","type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnuserlocation","kind":"symbol","title":"MLNUserLocation","role":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"The MLNUserLocation class defines a specific type of annotation that identifies","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the user’s current location. You do not create instances of this class","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"directly. Instead, you retrieve an existing ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNUserLocation","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" object from the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"code":"userLocation","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":" property of the map view displayed in your application.","type":"text"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNOverlay":{"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOverlay","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" protocol defines a specific type of annotation that represents"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"both a point and an area on a map. Overlay objects are essentially data objects"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"that contain the geographic data needed to represent the map area. Overlays can"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"take the form of a polyline or polygon."}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNOverlay","title":"MLNOverlay","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnoverlay","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"MLNOverlay","kind":"identifier"}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/objc(pl)NSObject":{"type":"unresolvable","title":"NSObject","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/objc(pl)NSObject"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNShapeSource":{"type":"topic","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource","kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" is a map content source that supplies vector shapes to be"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"shown on the map. The shapes may be instances of "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":","},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"or they may be defined by local or external"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"GeoJSON"},{"type":"text","text":" code. A shape source is added to an"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object along with an "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object. The vector style"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"layer defines the appearance of any content supplied by the shape source. You"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"can update a shape source by setting its "},{"code":"shape","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"code":"URL","type":"codeVoice"},{"type":"text","text":" property."}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnshapesource","fragments":[{"text":"MLNShapeSource","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"MLNShapeSource"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNAnnotation":{"title":"MLNAnnotation","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","role":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnannotation","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNAnnotation","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"type":"text","text":" protocol is used to provide annotation-related information"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to a map view. To use this protocol, you adopt it in any custom objects that"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"store or represent annotation data. Each object then serves as the source of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"information about a single map annotation and provides critical information,"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"such as the annotation’s location on the map. Annotation objects do not provide"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the visual representation of the annotation but typically coordinate (in"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"conjunction with the map view’s delegate) the creation of an appropriate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"objects to handle the display."}],"fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNAnnotation"}]},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNShape":{"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnshape","title":"MLNShape","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"MLNShape"}],"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","abstract":[{"type":"reference","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" is an abstract class that represents a shape or annotation. Shapes"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"constitute the content of a map — not only the overlays atop the map, but also"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the content that forms the base map."}],"kind":"symbol","type":"topic","role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNFeature":{"fragments":[{"text":"MLNFeature","kind":"identifier"}],"url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnfeature","kind":"symbol","type":"topic","title":"MLNFeature","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNFeature","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNFeature","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":"  protocol is used to provide details about geographic features"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"contained in an "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShapeSource","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" or "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNVectorTileSource","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object. Each concrete"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"subclass of "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNShape","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" in turn has a subclass that conforms to this protocol. A"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"feature object associates a shape with an optional identifier and attributes."}],"role":"symbol"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre":{"kind":"symbol","title":"MapLibre","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre","type":"topic","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Powerful, free and open-source mapping toolkit with full control over data sources and styling."}],"role":"collection","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre"},"doc://org.swift.MyProject/documentation/MapLibre/MLNVectorTileSource":{"type":"topic","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNVectorTileSource","abstract":[{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNVectorTileSource","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" is a map content source that supplies tiled vector data"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"in "},{"type":"text","text":"Mapbox Vector Tile"},{"type":"text","text":" format"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"to be shown on the map. The location of and metadata about the tiles are"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"defined either by an option dictionary or by an external file that conforms to"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"the"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"TileJSON specification"},{"type":"text","text":"."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"A vector tile source is added to an "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNStyle","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" object along with one or more"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/org.swift.MyProject\/documentation\/MapLibre\/MLNVectorStyleLayer","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" objects. A vector style layer defines the appearance of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"any content supplied by the vector tile source."}],"kind":"symbol","url":"\/documentation\/maplibre\/mlnvectortilesource","fragments":[{"text":"MLNVectorTileSource","kind":"identifier"}],"title":"MLNVectorTileSource"}}}